---
title: Pork Chops With Pepper Jam Pan Sauce plus Smoky Creamed Lentils & Roasted Carrots
description: Creamy, smoky, sweet, and savory, this meal elevates juicy pork chops with sweet and savory red pepper jam sauce. You’ll serve the saucy chops alongside tender lentils swirled with smoky red pepper crema and crème fraîche, and earthy roasted carrots. Sprinkle with scallion greens for a crisp, zippy garnish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66d70ff207a263836a73ea2b-7fb39228.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66d70ff207a263836a73ea2b-en-US.pdf
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pork-chops-with-pepper-jam-pan-sauce-66d70ff207a263836a73ea2b
nutrition:
  calories: 830 kcal
  fat: 39 g
